TITLE: These students in Texas won't be allowed to wear dresses or skirts after fifth grade
SUMMARY: A North Texas school district has updated its dress code for the upcoming school year to ban hooded clothing as well as dresses and skirts for many of its grade levels, reasoning that the change will help students in their future careers.

TITLE: Four libraries in New York reverse decision to pull LGBTQ book displays from children's sections
SUMMARY: A library board in New York reversed its decision to remove all LGBTQ-related displays from its children's section in four of its libraries during Pride month after the removal was criticized.
